		<p class="text--center" style="    color: #737373;">Already a member? <a href="/TrainerLogin/index">Login now</a> <svg class="icon"><use xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="assets/images/icons.svg#arrow-right"></use></svg></p>

